For the Run this application
pip install django
pip install djangorestframwork

---If you want to create superuser then fire this command
python manage.py createsuperuser

python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000

URLS for executing----------------

For Registration-----------
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/profile/
After Registration Token has been generated........

For Login-----------
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login/
After login you get token which represent in string format
copy that link and save it to browser(Modheader)
select request header and pass the values like
e.g.
Name - Authorization
value - Token asdfasdjfhkjadsfhkj

below api's the product,order,OrderItem can be perfrom like list of data,create of data and Update of data

After login the below api are executing----------
urls for product
http://127.0.0.1:8000/order/products/
urls for order
http://127.0.0.1:8000/order/orders/
urls for orderitem
http://127.0.0.1:8000/order/orderitem/


Note - Delete opeation not mention in code just
beacuse as per the IT rule the Delete fuctionality not provided in the system
but for the assignment it mention in comment section
orders-views-Product api
